<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in McKenzie Lake</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">McKenzie Lake is a well-established community full of beauty and overlooking the majestic Rocky Mountains and featuring a walking path overlooking beautiful Fish Creek Park. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The prime location on the borders of the lake is the most coveted and has a higher price bracket. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">This once prosperous farming community, McKenzie Lake is now an established neighbourhood offering good value and convenience to amenities, shopping, and transportation corridors.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The price range for single homes at McKenzie Lake real estate is between $275,000 to $3 million while condos are available for an average price of $307,130.</p>
        </div>
